{"type":"message","id":"bbe2ba8d","parentId":"3c65ac59","timestamp":"2026-02-18T12:12:29.579Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Verifying Pull Requests**\n\nI've successfully authenticated `gh`. The next step is to examine the pull requests. I'm focusing on #41, #42, #43, and #44. Currently, I'm checking each for potential conflicts.\n\n\n**Listing Pull Request Details**\n\nI'm now retrieving details for the listed pull requests. I've fetched the specifics for #41, #42, #43, and #44. Next, I'll proceed with verifying their individual statuses, starting with the technical ones.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771416749563_17","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"gh pr list --repo franklinbaldo/aparicio-funes --state open"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-gemini-cli","provider":"google-gemini-cli","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":878,"output":163,"cacheRead":4459,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":5500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771416745315}}
