{"type":"message","id":"164ffc07","parentId":"ba049c14","timestamp":"2026-02-18T12:12:39.231Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec_1771416758698_19","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"body\":\"Improved the PDF generation for 'Alfarrábios do Adi' to resemble a classic printed memoir.\\n\\nChanges:\\n- **CSS**: Adjusted margins to 25mm/20mm, enabled font ligatures, improved blockquote and image styling.\\n- **Script**: Added automatic Table of Contents generation for the complete book, updated footer template with page numbers, and refined HTML structure for better linking.\\n- **Documentation**: Created session logs and updated experience log for the Gutemberg agent.\\n\\n---\\n*PR created automatically by Jules for task [5513601199123664841](https://jules.google.com/task/5513601199123664841) started by @franklinbaldo*\",\"mergeable\":\"MERGEABLE\",\"title\":\"Refine PDF Layout and Typography\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":500,"aggregated":"{\"body\":\"Improved the PDF generation for 'Alfarrábios do Adi' to resemble a classic printed memoir.\\n\\nChanges:\\n- **CSS**: Adjusted margins to 25mm/20mm, enabled font ligatures, improved blockquote and image styling.\\n- **Script**: Added automatic Table of Contents generation for the complete book, updated footer template with page numbers, and refined HTML structure for better linking.\\n- **Documentation**: Created session logs and updated experience log for the Gutemberg agent.\\n\\n---\\n*PR created automatically by Jules for task [5513601199123664841](https://jules.google.com/task/5513601199123664841) started by @franklinbaldo*\",\"mergeable\":\"MERGEABLE\",\"title\":\"Refine PDF Layout and Typography\"}","cwd":"/home/franklinbaldo/.openclaw/agents/aparicio/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1771416759221}}
